@page
@model dynamic
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}
<section class="page-header">
    <h1>About COR0110268.11P</h1>
    <p>A universal governance core designed to bring structure, accountability, and transparency to any system.</p>
</section>

<section class="two-column">
    <div>
        <h2>Governance as an Engine</h2>
        <p>COR0110268.11P treats governance not as a static document, but as a living engine. Policies, rules, and oversight structures become executable components that can be configured, combined, and evolved.</p>
        <p>Instead of rebuilding governance from scratch for each domain, COR provides a shared foundation that can be specialized for defense, banking, AI, healthcare, and more.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h2>Core Principles</h2>
        <ul class="bullet-grid">
            <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> Every decision, rule, and exception is traceable.</li>
            <li><strong>Accountability:</strong> Roles, responsibilities, and approvals are explicit and enforceable.</li>
            <li><strong>Adaptability:</strong> Governance structures can evolve without breaking the system.</li>
            <li><strong>Neutrality:</strong> The engine is domain‑agnostic, ready to be shaped by your context.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
